# Project Structure

```
{{PROJECT_NAME}}/
├── {{SOURCE_DIR}}/          # Source code
├── {{CONFIG_DIR}}/          # Configuration
├── {{TEST_DIR}}/            # Tests
└── {{DOC_DIR}}/             # Documentation
```

## Directory Responsibilities
| Directory | Responsibility |
|-----------|----------------|
| `{{SOURCE_DIR}}/` | Main source code |
| `{{CONFIG_DIR}}/` | Configuration files |
| `{{TEST_DIR}}/` | Test files |
| `{{DOC_DIR}}/` | Documentation |
